            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header#faqHeading6
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqCollapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapse6")
                  | Will my insurance cover Suboxone or Methadone?
              #faqCollapse6.accordion-collapse.collapse(aria-labelledby="faqHeading6" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion")
                .accordion-body
                  | Most insurance plans in Washington cover medication-assisted treatment including Suboxone, Methadone, and Vivitrol. Apple Health covers these medications at 100% with no copay. Learn more about 
                  a(href="/blog/medication-assisted-treatment-spokane.html") MAT options in Spokane
                  | .

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header#faqHeading7
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqCollapse7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapse7")
